OL,3,CDrug-fuelled patient assaults NHS
OL,4,Cstaff after ripping tubes from baby
OL,6,FA man who violently attacked and
OL,7,Finjured two nurses after pulling life-
OL,8,Fsaving equipment from a seriously ill
OL,9,Fbaby has been jailed.
OL,11,FAndrew Phillips, 26, became aggressive
OL,12,Fwhile being treated in Blackpool
OL,13,FVictoria Hospital resus department.
OL,15,FPreston Crown Court heard that
OL,16,FPhillips was believed to have taken
OL,17,Fcocaine prior to the incident and
OL,18,Frepeatedly ignored staff instructions.
