OL,3,CDrug-fuelled patient assaults NHS
OL,4,Cstaff after ripping tubes from baby
OL,6,FHe forced his way into a treatment
OL,7,Fcubicle where an 11-month-old baby was
OL,8,Freceiving critical care, despite
OL,9,Fwarnings to stay away.
OL,11,FOnce inside, Phillips threw a chair
OL,12,Fand then fell into the infant's bed,
OL,13,Fyanking out the baby's IV line and
OL,14,Foxygen tube.
OL,16,FIn a desperate attempt to protect the
OL,17,Fbaby, a paramedic and two nurses
OL,18,Frushed to intervene.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
