OL,3,CDrug-fuelled patient assaults NHS
OL,4,Cstaff after ripping tubes from baby
OL,6,FDuring the struggle, Phillips pulled
OL,7,Fone nurse's arm, fracturing her arm
OL,8,Fand wrist. He then lashed out at
OL,9,Fothers, punching and kicking staff,
OL,10,Fleaving another nurse with a bruised
OL,11,Fankle.
OL,13,FLancashire Police said that despite
OL,14,Fthe chaos, the baby was not harmed.
OL,16,FPhillips, of Grange Road in Blackpool,
OL,17,Fpleaded guilty to inflicting grievous
OL,18,Fbodily harm, assault causing actual
OL,19,Fbodily harm, and affray. He was handed
OL,20,Fan extended sentence of four-and-a-
OL,21,Fhalf years in prison.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
