OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F395A1750231382
OL,3,CDrug-fuelled patient assaults NHS
OL,4,Cstaff after ripping tubes from baby
OL,6,FDetective Constable Alexa Taylor of
OL,7,FBlackpool CID, said: "I welcome the
OL,8,Fprison sentence imposed on Andrew
OL,9,FPhillips.
OL,11,F"I hope the sentence sends a clear
OL,12,Fmessage that the police and courts
OL,13,Fwill not tolerate disturbances on
OL,14,Fhospital grounds and attacks on our
OL,15,Fcolleagues within the NHS.
OL,17,F"Hospitals, NHS staff and paramedics
OL,18,Fprovide care to the sick, injured and
OL,19,Fvulnerable, and should not be
OL,20,Fassaulted or put at risk while they
OL,21,Fare working."
